  <brief_title>VentrAssistTM LVAD as a Bridge to Cardiac Transplantation - Pivotal Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the VentrAssistTM Left Ventricular Assist Device as a Bridge to Cardiac Transplantation - Pivotal Trial</official_title>
